<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:180px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/wikipedia-shigastan/%E3%82%B7%E3%82%AC%E3%82%B9%E3%82%BF%E3%83%B3%E5%AE%98%E9%82%B8.jpg" style="width:180px;" alt="シガスタン官邸.jpg" class="image" />
